alluxio.master.file.meta

Class InodeDirectory

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.master.file.meta.Inode<InodeDirectory>
      • alluxio.master.file.meta.InodeDirectory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JournalEntryRepresentable

    @NotThreadSafe
public final class InodeDirectory
extends Inode<InodeDirectory>
    Alluxio file system's directory representation in the file system master. The inode must be locked (Inode.lockRead() or Inode.lockWrite()) before methods are called.
